ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectHog Industry Loan Loss Reserve Program
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to establish the Hog Industry Loan Loss Reserve Program and to provide for federal contributions to financial institutions to increase the availability of loans to Canadian hog producers.
